PRODUCT + COMMERCE
═══════════════════════════════════════════

PRODUCTS: 5 designs × 2 colorways = 10 SKUs
- The Frontier (Lamb) — Midnight Black / Tobacco
- The Warden (Lamb) — Midnight Black / Cognac  
- The Nomad (Lamb) — Midnight / Sand
- The Heir (Lamb) — Black / Ivory
- The Sentinel (Camel) — Natural / Bark
Types: src/types/product.ts
Data: src/content/products/ (JSON files)

FOLDER RULES:
- Page sections (used once): src/components/sections/
- Reusable atoms: src/components/ui/
- Product components: src/components/product/
- Layout: src/components/layout/

COMPONENT RULES:
- Mobile first always — design for 390px then scale up
- Use container-luxury class for max-width + padding
- Use section-padding for vertical section rhythm
- Images: always next/image with explicit width/height and meaningful alt text
- Placeholder images: use aspect-ratio divs with bg-void-2 until photos arrive

